articles.title: ODI World Cup digest: Saud stars for Pakistan; Dharamsala-Delhi double; Gill in doubt - ESPNcricinfo
articles.description: Pakistan do enough to beat Netherlands, a Dharamsala-Delhi double-header looms on Saturday, while Shubman Gill is in doubt to face Australia
